urope, [AS] Asia, [OA] Oceania, [NA] North America, [SA] South America, [AN] Antarctica','deliang.feng@ecarxgroup.com',0,'property type 以中国香港为例，值为  AS|CHN|HKG；以德国为例值为 EU|DEU， 如果不能获取到国家一级需要给到大洲一级，比如EU。横跨欧亚大陆的俄罗斯可以定义为值 EU|AS|RUS。 Note：由于不同厂商的目标市场定义区别较大，可能按语言、宗教或者其他属性划分，不是所有的区划都有ISO标准定义。 业务扩展时可以直接在将属性字符串添加在前面，比如需要判断是否是亚太经合组织，对于目标市场为香港的返回值应该定义为类似 APEC|AS|CHN|HKG这样的字符，只要添加的属性APEC不与大洲的两位字母简写，以及iso-3166-1国家地区码存在重复值即可。',17,'2024-07-09 17:34:31','',1),(357,91392,'CHARGING_ENDURANCE_MILEAGE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Float','ISensor','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','充电限制电量(SOC)可行驶距离，单位 km','Endurance mileage base on Charging SOC, unit: km ','tao.zhan@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-07-09 17:36:04','',1),(358,91648,'DISCHARGING_ENDURANCE_MILEAGE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Float','ISensor','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','放电限制电量(SOC)可行驶距离，单位 km','Endurance mileage base on Discharging SOC, unit: km','tao.zhan@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-07-09 17:37:13','',1),(361,92416,'FUEL_WARNING_COLOR','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Enum','ISensor','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','油量图标警告颜色','Oil level icon warning color','tao.zhan@ecarxgroup.com',0,'FuelWarningColor',16,'2024-07-09 17:43:36','',1),(362,92672,'POWER_FLOW_NOTICE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Enum','ICharging','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','驻车充电通知，原ID:HYBRID_FUNC_POWER_FLOW_NOTICE','Try to parking charging notice ','tao.zhan@ecarxgroup.com',0,'PowerFlowNotice',16,'2024-07-09 17:50:40','',1),(363,92928,'BATTERY_SOC','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Float','ICharging','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','电池充电模式 SOC(目标电量),原ID：HYBRID_FUNC_BATTERY_SOC','Set/get Adding battery mode HYBRID_FUNC_BATTERY_SAVE_MODE or HYBRID_FUNC_BATTERY_CHARGE_MODE SOC','tao.zhan@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-07-09 17:54:22','',1),(367,939