，根据ICC反馈可设置的时区的结果进行比对，只有一致时才执行实际的设置时区命令。','Preset time zone<br> CSC pre-set the time zone with ICC and compares the results of the available time zones based on ICC feedback. Only when they are consistent, will the actual time zone setting command be executed.','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'TimeZone',17,'2024-08-20 23:17:17','',1),(511,130816,'GNSS_LOCATOR_AUTH_CYCLE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Integer','GNSS','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','定位上传云端授权天数，单位：天，原ID：SETTING_FUNC_CAR_TCAM_LOCATOR_AUTH_CYCLE, 获取支持哪些天数用ICarConfig.getSupportValues()，返回示例： 90 180 360','Location upload cloud authorization days','hang.jiang@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-08-22 10:59:25','',1),(512,131072,'GNSS_LOCATOR_UPDATE_AUTH_TIME','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Integer[]','GNSS','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','定位上传云端的授权开始时间，示例：Integer[] startTime = {2024, 8, 21}，原ID：SETTING_FUNC_CAR_TCAM_LOCATOR_UPDATE_AUTH_TIME','Starting time of authorization for uploading to the cloud location','hang.jiang@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-08-22 11:03:06','',1),(513,131328,'AUTO_SEAT_HEATING_TIME','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT','Enum','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','自动座椅加热时间设置','the auto start seat heating time setting with VehicleSeat<br>may use for Auto climate setting<br>','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'AutoSeatHeatingTime',16,'2024-08-22 15:03:37','',0),(514,131584,'HVAC_CLEAN_ZONE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Enum','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','CLEANZONE 不可用时，图标显示为置灰状态;只有满足所有以下条件时，显示开启工作：1.所有车门和尾门关闭；2.所有车窗关闭；3.空调风扇已启动；4.内外循环为AUTO模式；否则显示未开启工作。','When CLEANZONE is unavailable, the icon displays in a grayed out state; Only when all of the following conditions are met, will the opening work be displayed: 1. All car doors and tailgate are closed; 2. All car windows are closed; 3. The air conditioning fan has started; 4. The internal and external circulation is in AUTO mode; Otherwise, it will display as not working.','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'CleanZoneState',16,'2024-08-22 15:11:03','',1),(515,131840,'HVAC_AIR_FRAGRANCE','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT','Boolean','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','香氛功能开启和关闭。（和香氛浓度等级重合，处于废弃状态）','to turn On or Off air fragrance','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'',16,'2024-08-22 15:12:15','',1),(516,132096,'HVAC_AIR_FRAGRANCE_SLOT','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Enum','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','选择并启动具体的香氛槽','The setting to select(active) fragrance slot','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',1,'AirFragranceSlot',16,'2024-08-22 15:15:41','',1),(517,132352,'HVAC_AIR_FRAGRANCE_LEVEL','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT','Enum','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','香氛浓度等级设置.香氛槽与AREA对应关系参考 {@link AirFragranceSlot}.不区分则传VehicleAreaSeat#SEAT_ROW_1_LEFT','to set air fragrance level.','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'AirFragranceLevel',16,'2024-08-22 15:20:12','',1),(518,132608,'HVAC_FRAGRANCE_MARGIN','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_SEAT','Integer','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','香氛剩余量，取值范围0~100。香氛槽域AREA对应关系参考 {@link AirFragranceSlot}','fragrance residue,fragrance remaining percentage, rang from 0 to 100','jian2.min@ecarxgroup.com',0,'0～100',16,'2024-08-22 15:21:40','',1),(519,132864,'HVAC_AUTO_DRY','VEHICLE_AREA_TYPE_GLOBAL','Boolean','IHvac','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_ACCESS_READ_WRITE','VEHICLE_PROPERTY_CHANGE_MODE_ONCHANGE','锁车空调自干燥。车辆行驶下电锁车后，空调可能会自主运行鼓风机一定时间，吹出蒸发器和风道中的冷凝水，防止水积聚产生霉味污染座舱。','The air conditioner dries automatically when the vehicle is locked. After the vehicle is electrically locked while driving, the air conditioner may automatically run the blower for a certain period of time to blow out the condensed water in the evaporator and air duct to prevent water accumulation and moldy odor from contaminating